      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Hard to knock the form of ROLINGINTHEDEEP (3) who stretched his winning streak to four by leading to score by close to 2m at this circuit and distance last time. Kept up to the mark with a trial since and draws well enough to go forward again so can continue the winning run. ALWAYS BE BLAKEY (8) came from this same barrier to make a winning return here a fortnight ago. Drops to a distance where his strike rate is strong and has won when second-up before so could go on with it. ODIN (4) had to work last start but had been producing some good efforts prior including a Bendigo win and a second from this barrier at this venue. Usually in the money when he races at this circuit and distance. Contender. BLAKE BOLAC (9) broke last time but wasn't far away when fresh prior and could be ready to peak third up.",
